3,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"富貴檢疫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文華東方 娛樂套房 = $51,150 (雙人)<br />\n<br />\n特大號床|167平方米 / 1798平方呎|市區景觀<br />\n此豪華套房能讓人富有格調地盡情娛樂，同時享受私人避風港。<br />\n<br />\n這套多功能的套房專為娛樂活動、產品發佈會和 VIP 住宿而設。套房配備最先進的影音設施、85 吋 LED 電視、娛樂牆和設有 FreshBed 睡眠系統的主臥室。<br />\n<br />\n主臥室內設休息和更衣區、步入式衣櫃、FreshBed 睡眠系統和配備迷人雲石浴缸的獨立套廁。客廳則配有先進的科技產品，包括娛樂牆、VR 和 PlayStation 遊戲設備。您可以在能容納多達 8 位賓客就座的飯廳內享用大廚於 Gaggenau 廚房炮製的米芝蓮星級餐飲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photos.mandarinoriental.com/is/image/MandarinOriental/landmark-rooms-entertainment-suite-living-room?wid=4000&amp;fmt=jpeg,rgb&amp;qlt=63,0&amp;op_sharpen=0&amp;resMode=sharp2&amp;op_usm=0,0,0,0&amp;icc=sRGB%20IEC61966-2.1&amp;iccEmbed=1&amp;printRes=72&amp;fit=wrap&amp;qlt=45,0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotos.mandarinoriental.com%2Fis%2Fimage%2FMandarinOriental%2Flandmark-rooms-entertainment-suite-living-room%3Fwid%3D4000%26fmt%3Djpeg%2Crgb%26qlt%3D63%2C0%26op_sharpen%3D0%26resMode%3Dsharp2%26op_usm%3D0%2C0%2C0%2C0%26icc%3DsRGB%2520IEC61966-2.1%26iccEmbed%3D1%26printRes%3D72%26fit%3Dwrap%26qlt%3D45%2C0&h=93e9ba74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photos.mandarinoriental.com/is/image/MandarinOriental/landmark-rooms-entertainment-suite-bedroom?wid=4000&amp;fmt=jpeg,rgb&amp;qlt=63,0&amp;op_sharpen=0&amp;resMode=sharp2&amp;op_usm=0,0,0,0&amp;icc=sRGB%20IEC61966-2.1&amp;iccEmbed=1&amp;printRes=72&amp;fit=wrap&amp;qlt=45,0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotos.mandarinoriental.com%2Fis%2Fimage%2FMandarinOriental%2Flandmark-rooms-entertainment-suite-bedroom%3Fwid%3D4000%26fmt%3Djpeg%2Crgb%26qlt%3D63%2C0%26op_sharpen%3D0%26resMode%3Dsharp2%26op_usm%3D0%2C0%2C0%2C0%26icc%3DsRGB%2520IEC61966-2.1%26iccEmbed%